el Francis, Rose shows how such thinkers are animated by religious aspirations and anxieties that are ultimately in tension with Christian teachings and the secular values those teachings birthed in modernity.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Aug 2021) 0aConservatismxPhilosophy. 0aConservatismxReligious aspects. 7aPOLITICAL SCIENCE / Political Ideologies / Conservatism & Liberalism.2bisacsh40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300263084423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9780300263084.jpg  aGBV-deGruyter-alles